window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Unexpected enemies, unlikely alliances, and one struggling reaper. </p> <p>The Earth crystal is missing, and I have no clue who took it. To make matters worse, the Council knows about my forbidden abilities. They still want my help to find the remaining artifacts, which means hey must be desperate...but for what? </p> <p>Now I’ve partnered up with Charlie, my deceased best friend’s brother. The only problem is that he blames me for his sister’s death. I just hope this isn’t one more thing that will blow up in my face. I’ve had enough of that the past month to last the rest of my life. </p> <p>As the truth begins to unravel, the pressure of making the right choices lands square on my shoulders. If I make one wrong decision, the world as we know it will be over. </p> <p>White Raven meets the Artifact Hunters in <i>Reaper of Wings</i>, a paranormal listen for those who love a dark twist. </p>"; 
